        <div class="explanation">
            <h3>ðŸ“ Hvordan bruker jeg kalkulatoren?</h3>
            <p><strong>Steg 1:</strong> Finn bookmaker odds (f.eks. Pinnacle) for samme utfall</p>
            <p><strong>Steg 2:</strong> Finn bookmakerens payout-prosent (vanligvis 91-95%)</p>
            <p><strong>Steg 3:</strong> Noter Polymarket-prisen (i cent, f.eks. 56Â¢)</p>
            <p><strong>Steg 4:</strong> Bestem hvor mye du vil satse</p>
        </div>
        <form id="evCalculator" autocomplete="off">
            <div class="input-group">
                <label for="bookmakerOdds">Bookmaker Odds (desimal, f.eks. 2.0):</label>
                <input type="text" id="bookmakerOdds" placeholder="2.0">
            </div>
