        <div class="explanation">
            <h3>ðŸ§  Formel Forklaring:</h3>
            <div class="formula">
                EV = (Antall Shares) Ã— (Din Sannsynlighet - Polymarket Pris i dollar)
            </div>
            <p><strong>Hvor:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Antall Shares:</strong> Innsats Ã· (Polymarket Pris Ã· 100)</li>
                <li><strong>Din Sannsynlighet:</strong> 1 Ã· Edge-justerte Odds</li>
                <li><strong>Edge-justerte Odds:</strong> Bookmaker Odds Ã· (Payout % Ã· 100)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="warning">
            <strong>âš ï¸ Viktig:</strong> Kalkulatoren antar at bookmaker-oddsen er \"sann\" sannsynlighet etter edge-justering.
        </div>
